After signing out and going directly to [SAC | https://support.atlassian.com] the links work fine.

Tested on:
- Note 3 android {{4.3}} device, with kernel version {{3.4.0-1670611}}, Chrome {{39.0.2171.93}}
- Moto X Android version {{4.4.2}}, kernel {{3.4.42}}, and Chrome version {{39.0.2171.59}}


